      "attributes": {
        "name": "Shaper",
        "description": "Shapers run.\nThey don’t run for money, they don’t run for change. They run because they can. They run for fame, for notoriety, for fun. They run because, to them, it is the purest form of self-expression. It’s a challenge, to tinker together the perfect program, to find the most efficient solution to their problems. Though it may take some time for them to find the correct solution, once they do they can crack any server. The contents of the server don’t matter.\nAll that matters is the run.",
